title: Rosetta Stone Hebrew V3 Parts 1 AND 2 ISO
description:
I'm not claiming to have ripped these ISO's but I did happen to find them onand took quite a while to get all the pieces.....

I installed them both and they work perfectly.

This should be the first time the V3 Hebrew is available on a torrent site. Please seed as I can't for too long....


If you've cracked your rosetta stone it should work fine, it may come up asking for an activation code, but just X out of that window when it does, and it'll work.
